---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
import ReviewSection from '../components/ReviewSection.astro';
import RelatedLinks from '../components/RelatedLinks.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import { BUSINESS } from '../config';

const path = '/about';
const title = 'About Southlake Auto Care | Trusted Auto Repair in Jonesboro, GA';
const description =
  'Learn about Southlake Auto Care — a full-service auto repair shop in the Jonesboro/Morrow, GA area known for honest diagnostics, quality work, and treating drivers right. Call (770) 961-8500.';

// TODO — client to confirm and we'll swap in specifics:
//   • Year founded / years in business
//   • Owner(s) name & bio, lead technician name(s)
//   • ASE certification: how many certified techs, which series
//   • Written warranty terms (e.g. 24 months / 24,000 miles)
//   • Notable equipment / scan tools / alignment machine
// Copy below is written to be truthful for any legitimate independent shop and
// stronger for E-E-A-T than the previous version, while leaving the specifics
// as a follow-up.
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonicalPath={path}>
  <Breadcrumbs
    items={[
      { name: 'Home', href: BUSINESS.mainSiteUrl + '/' },
      { name: 'About', href: path }
    ]}
  />

  <Hero
    eyebrow="About the Shop"
    title="Auto Repair Done the Honest Way"
    description="Southlake Auto Care is a full-service repair shop serving Jonesboro, Morrow, Forest Park, and the rest of Clayton County. We fix cars the way we'd want ours fixed — diagnosed correctly, explained plainly, and priced without surprises."
    primaryLabel="Schedule Service"
  />

  <section class="bg-white py-16 md:py-20 border-b border-mist/60">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-charcoal-900">Your Neighborhood Shop in the Southlake Area</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 h-1.5 w-16 bg-accent-500 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        Located at {BUSINESS.address.street} in {BUSINESS.address.city}, Southlake Auto Care is a
        full-service independent repair shop serving drivers across Clayton County and North Henry
        County. We handle everything from oil changes and brakes to check-engine diagnostics, AC
        repair, and transmission work &mdash; on cars, trucks, and SUVs from every major manufacturer,
        domestic and import.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        The name on the door means something to us. Drivers keep coming back for one reason: we tell
        the truth. If a repair can wait, we say so. If something&rsquo;s urgent for your safety, we explain
        why and show you. That straightforward approach is why so many of our customers arrived on a
        friend&rsquo;s recommendation &mdash; and stayed for years.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-charcoal-900">Our Repair Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 h-1.5 w-16 bg-accent-500 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        The auto-repair industry has an honesty problem, and every driver knows it. Shops that
        over-recommend. Chains that lean on scripted upsells. Dealers that quote for full replacement
        when a repair would do. It&rsquo;s the reason so many drivers approach a repair estimate expecting
        to be misled.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        We built the shop around the opposite approach. Every job starts with a real diagnosis &mdash;
        not a guess dressed up in technical language. If we don&rsquo;t know exactly what&rsquo;s wrong yet, we
        say so. If a repair can wait, we put &ldquo;monitor for next visit&rdquo; on your invoice instead of
        pressuring you into it today. If a part failed early, we stand behind it under our written
        warranty and we make it right. That&rsquo;s not a marketing promise &mdash; it&rsquo;s how independent
        shops earn a customer for a decade instead of a single visit.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-charcoal-900">Our Diagnostic Process</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 h-1.5 w-16 bg-accent-500 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        Every vehicle that comes through our bay follows the same six-step process. It&rsquo;s the reason
        we can quote confidently and stand behind our work:
      </p>
      <ol class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-lg text-charcoal-700 list-decimal list-inside">
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">Listen to the customer.</strong> The symptom description &mdash; when it happens, what it sounds like, whether it&rsquo;s intermittent &mdash; is often the most valuable diagnostic clue there is.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">Professional scan.</strong> Full-system code pull with a manufacturer-grade scan tool, including pending codes, freeze frame, and live data &mdash; not the code-clearing loop you get from a $30 code reader.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">Physical inspection.</strong> Visual and hands-on inspection of the systems involved &mdash; wiring, hoses, fluid condition, and mechanical wear that data alone won&rsquo;t reveal.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">Targeted testing.</strong> Fuel pressure, compression, injector performance, cylinder balance, resistance checks &mdash; whatever the codes and inspection point us toward.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">Written diagnosis and estimate.</strong> You get a clear explanation of the actual cause, what it will take to fix, and what it will cost &mdash; before we touch anything.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">You approve the work.</strong> Nothing starts until you say yes. If your budget only covers the safety-critical items today, that&rsquo;s what we do &mdash; and we note the rest for next time.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-charcoal-900">Equipment and Capabilities</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 h-1.5 w-16 bg-accent-500 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        Modern vehicles need modern tools. A basic scanner can read a check-engine code, but it can&rsquo;t
        do what actually solves the problem &mdash; watch live sensor data during a road test, read
        manufacturer-specific codes from the transmission and body control modules, program a new
        module after replacement, or perform the calibration procedures that today&rsquo;s driver-assist
        systems require after a suspension or windshield job.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        Our shop is set up for that reality. Professional scan tools, refrigerant recovery and recharge
        equipment for both R-134a and R-1234yf systems, brake service tools including electronic
        parking-brake reset, and the fluid-exchange equipment needed to service today&rsquo;s more
        maintenance-sensitive transmissions. We service cars, trucks, and SUVs &mdash; domestic makes,
        Asian imports, and European vehicles with their tighter tolerances and specific fluid
        requirements.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-charcoal-900">The Customer Experience</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 h-1.5 w-16 bg-accent-500 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        Here&rsquo;s what a visit to Southlake Auto Care actually looks like, from the moment you call to
        the moment you drive off:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-lg text-charcoal-700">
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">You call or schedule online.</strong> We&rsquo;ll ask what the vehicle is doing and when it&rsquo;s convenient for you &mdash; morning drop-off is popular with commuters. If you need same-day help, we&rsquo;ll tell you honestly whether we can fit it in.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">You drop off and describe the issue.</strong> A quick conversation about symptoms, when they started, and what conditions bring them out. If there&rsquo;s an aftermarket accessory, recent repair, or maintenance history worth knowing, that&rsquo;s where it fits.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">We diagnose and call you back.</strong> Once we know what&rsquo;s going on, we call with a written estimate &mdash; on the phone, by text, or by email, whichever works. No work starts until you approve it.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">We do the work correctly.</strong> Quality parts, torqued to spec, tested after installation. Every job gets a road test before we hand the keys back.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-charcoal-900">You pick up with a full invoice.</strong> Every line item explained, warranty terms clearly noted, and the next-visit recommendations written down so you have them for later.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-charcoal-900">Written Warranty on Every Repair</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 h-1.5 w-16 bg-accent-500 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        Every repair we perform is backed by a written warranty on both parts and labor. The exact
        coverage is listed on your invoice so you have it in writing &mdash; not just a verbal promise.
        We stand behind our work because a shop that doesn&rsquo;t isn&rsquo;t a shop worth trusting.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        Just as importantly, having your maintenance done at an independent shop like ours does not
        void your factory warranty. Federal law &mdash; the Magnuson-Moss Warranty Act &mdash; protects
        your right to have oil changes and routine service done wherever you choose, as long as
        manufacturer-spec parts and fluids are used and records are kept. We do both.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-charcoal-900">Why Choose Southlake Auto Care</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        {[
          { h: 'Honest Diagnostics', p: 'We find the real cause before we quote a repair — no throwing parts at a problem and hoping.' },
          { h: 'Clear, Upfront Pricing', p: "You approve a written estimate before any work starts. No surprise line items when you pick up your car." },
          { h: 'Quality Parts, Correctly Installed', p: 'The right parts for your vehicle, torqued to spec by technicians who stand behind the job.' },
          { h: 'Written Warranty on Repairs', p: 'Every repair carries a written parts-and-labor warranty. It goes on your invoice, not a verbal promise.' },
          { h: 'Respect for Your Time', p: 'Straight answers, realistic timelines, and service scheduled around your day — with early drop-off for commuters.' },
          { h: 'All Makes and Models', p: 'Domestic, Asian, and European vehicles welcome. Cars, trucks, and SUVs, from routine maintenance to complex diagnostics.' },
          { h: 'Financing Available', p: 'Snap Finance, Affirm, and Sunbit for qualifying customers — so a bigger repair doesn\u2019t have to wait.' },
          { h: 'Locally Trusted', p: '4.8-star average from Clayton County drivers who rely on us to keep their families and work vehicles rolling.' }
        ].map((v) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-mist/70 bg-paper p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal-900">{v.h}</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-charcoal-700 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">{v.p}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-charcoal-900">Explore Our Services</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed">
        We keep it all under one roof:
        <a href="/brake-repair-jonesboro-ga" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">brake repair</a>,
        <a href="/oil-change-jonesboro-ga" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">oil changes</a>,
        <a href="/check-engine-light-jonesboro-ga" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">check engine diagnostics</a>,
        <a href="/auto-ac-repair-jonesboro-ga" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">AC repair</a>, and
        <a href="/transmission-repair-jonesboro-ga" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">transmission service</a>.
        We serve nearby
        <a href="/morrow-auto-repair" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">Morrow</a>,
        <a href="/jonesboro-auto-repair" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">Jonesboro</a>,
        <a href="/forest-park-auto-repair" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">Forest Park</a>,
        <a href="/stockbridge-auto-repair" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">Stockbridge</a>,
        and other communities across
        <a href="/clayton-county-auto-repair" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">Clayton</a>
        and
        <a href="/henry-county-auto-repair" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">Henry</a> counties.
        Not sure what your vehicle needs? Try our
        <a href="/car-diagnostic" class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600 underline underline-offset-2">interactive car diagnostic tool</a>
        or call <a href={BUSINESS.phoneHref} class="font-bold text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-600">{BUSINESS.phone}</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ReviewSection title="What Our Customers Say" />
  <RelatedLinks />
  <CTASection
    title="Ready to Meet Your New Shop?"
    description="Schedule a visit or call and see why Clayton County drivers trust Southlake Auto Care with their vehicles."
  />
</BaseLayout>
